          "text": "（同新水令） 嗳，他闹一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈哈哈，啊，他笑一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闹一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王留",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闹一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有什么热闹，学与爷爷听啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，还有哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同雁儿落） 见几个粉搽的白面皮横拴着油鬏髻，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他笑一声便打一棒锤，跳一跳高似田地。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同夹白） 爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同川拨棹） 好叫我便笑，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同夹白） 咦，哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同川拨棹） 哎呀微微。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "装着一个鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人多我也看不得仔细。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同七兄弟） 我走到这壁那壁，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百般样儿千般戏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，百般样儿千般戏，还有什么热闹，学来爷爷听听啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，只见一个人儿，手提着墨线儿，他叫这个这个……这个这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们倒是说呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，我们忘啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个人儿，手提着墨线儿，噢，想这个么，你们说的不是耍傀儡的罢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对啦，是耍傀儡的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，学与爷爷听啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王留",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胖姑学呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王留来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同梅花酒） 哎它，它唤做甚傀儡，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "它唤做甚魁垒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "墨线儿穿的红白粉儿装的什么样的东西嗖嗖的呼啸起咚咚的鼓声催，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同夹白） 爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同梅花酒） 他坐着吃堂食，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺立着看筵席。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要吃也不得吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同收江南） 呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可正是席前花影座闲移。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀，把我累坏了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，我们饿了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们饿了，后面去吃饸饹去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胖姑、王留",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胖姑 （煞尾） 雨余云罢芝麻地，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王留 （夹白） 爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 我到那沤麻坑里洗个澡去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡老头 （夹白） 不许去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胖姑 （煞尾） 唐三藏今日取经去，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 都是俺胖姑儿从头到尾告诉了你。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胖姑跑下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘟，嘟，嘟。你瞧，又给打哭啦。王留儿不要哭啦，叫我么，你答应，他还不"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打你，起来到后面吃饸饹去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王留",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷背着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃，这么大还叫背着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王留",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷背着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我偌大年纪，背不动了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王留",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷背着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡老头",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "淘气。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡老头背王留下。）"
        }
